snippet.title: TWISTEX - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
TWISTEX is a falling block puzzle game with a 'twist'. Made especially for VR, it combines classic gameplay with original, new mechanics.

Wishlist Now!
Oculus/Meta Store: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/5761208457328437?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=launch

SteamVR version coming later 2023
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2518940/TWISTEX?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=launch

Join the discord server to get involved, or follow the socials for the latest updates.
